The Telegraph - Calcutta (Kolkata) | Sports | In the City
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     IN THE CITY
                  
	 Former India player Krishnendu Roy will coach Bengal for the 62nd Santosh Trophy scheduled to be held in Jammu amp; Kashmir from May 25. Roy will be joined by ex-India goalkeeper Tarun Bose as the goalkeeping coach. The squad is yet to be announced. Defending champions Punjab and runners up Bengal along with semi-finalists Kerala and Maharashtra have been directly qualified to the last eight.                 
	 Mohammedan Sporting avoided relegation with an 87-run win over Burnpur United in the CAB relegation play- off final match on Friday.       
	Brief scores      
	Mohammedan Sporting 301. Burnpur United 214. Mohammedan Sporting won by 87 runs.                
	 Prafulla Chandra College beat Jaipuria College by four wickets in a Calcutta University College tournament match on Friday.      
	Brief scores      
	Jaipuria College 277/7. Prafulla Chandra College 278/6 (Mohammed Iqbal Ali 84 n.o.) Prafulla Chandra College won by 4 wkts.                
	 YMCA (Green) made the last eight of the Gupta Memorial inter-club table tennis championships beating Friends Staff D (HG) and Bhowanipore Bayam Samity A in the junior division group A match at Khudiram Anusilan Kendra on Friday.                
	 The DLF-Saturday Club Sports Carnival began at the club premises on Friday. Ten city clubs are vying for top honours in the nine-day meet.                
	TABLE TENNIS: Inter-club meet at Khudiram Anusilan Kendra from 2 pm.                                                                                                                                                                     
